thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by William Mcphee

author: William Mcphee
title: William Mcphee
text: Used Omega Aukland on both occasions on holiday from uk. On returning, they do not nit pick over minor marks or defects that were there previously & possibly overlooked. Other firms are known not to mark hidden defects but 'discover' them on return. Feb2017
